Patch

I didn't put the code in the CDOFeatureDelta.write because it is only necessary in the case where we change the state of an object (client).

Changing the state of an object during the serialization process... it is kind of weird.

Also, I would like to use the same serialization when we will notify other session with the delta. In this case we do not need to change the state of the cdorevision.

I created a visitor that does the job. For a single reference it is fast....
For a many relationship... I need to go through the list :-( I have no choice.


